== 製作 ==
2014年4月4日，[[基努·李維|基努·李維]]加入劇組飾演一名在周末獨自留家的好男人。之後登門拜訪的兩位美女卻將她的生活搞得天翻地覆<ref name=Reeves>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Keanu Reeves, Eli Roth To Team On Thriller ‘Knock Knock’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/04/keanu-reeves-eli-roth-to-team-on-thriller-knock-knock-709894/|accessdate=August 18, 2014|publisher=deadline.com|date=April 4, 2014|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703080728/http://deadline.com/2014/04/keanu-reeves-eli-roth-to-team-on-thriller-knock-knock-709894/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。智利女演員{{link-en|伊格內西亞·阿拉芒|Ignacia Allamand}}也加入本片的演出<ref name=Allamand>{{cite news|last1=Phillips|first1=Chaka|title=Eli Roth New Movie: 'Knock Knock' To Star Keanu Reeves; Film To Debut In September?|url=http://www.latinpost.com/articles/10525/20140414/eli-roth-new-movie-knock-star-keanu-reeves-film-debut.htm|accessdate=August 18, 2014|publisher=latinpost.com|date=April 14, 2014|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621055658/http://www.latinpost.com/articles/10525/20140414/eli-roth-new-movie-knock-star-keanu-reeves-film-debut.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月26日，[[獅門娛樂|獅門娛樂]]獲得了電影的經銷權<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Lionsgate Closes Eli Roth-Keanu Reeves Thriller ‘Knock Knock’ At $2.5 Million|url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/knock-knock-keanu-reeves-lionsgate-eli-roth-sundance-1201359861/|accessdate=January 27, 2015|publisher=deadline.com|date=January 26, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601094356/http://deadline.com/2015/01/knock-knock-keanu-reeves-lionsgate-eli-roth-sundance-1201359861/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
拍攝開始於2014年4月14日在[[智利|智利]][[聖地牙哥|聖地牙哥]]進行<ref>{{cite news|title=Keanu Reeves snapped by paparazzi while filming in Chile|url=http://www.channel24.co.za/Paparazzi/Paparazzi-Keanu-Reeves-spotted-filming-in-Chile-20140415|accessdate=August 18, 2014|publisher=channel24.co.za|date=April 15, 2014|archive-date=2015-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404073047/http://www.channel24.co.za/Paparazzi/Paparazzi-Keanu-Reeves-spotted-filming-in-Chile-20140415|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2014年5月11日完成拍攝<ref>{{cite web|title=Keanu Reeves finished filming his movie "Knock Knock" in Chile|url=https://twitter.com/okka_nyan/status/465429794251755521/photo/1|publisher=twitter.com|accessdate=August 18, 2014|date=May 11, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213515/https://twitter.com/okka_nyan/status/465429794251755521/photo/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
2015年1月23日，電影在[[聖丹斯電影節|聖丹斯電影節]]上首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/jason-segel-tour-wows-sundance-article-1.2090529|title=Jason Segel’s 'The End of the Tour' wows at Sundance|work=NY Daily News|accessdate=25 January 2015|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107031356/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/jason-segel-tour-wows-sundance-article-1.2090529|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並預計於2015年10月9日在美國上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lionsgatepublicity.com/theatrical/knockknock/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-07-25 |archive-date=2017-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819062012/http://www.lionsgatepublicity.com/theatrical/knockknock/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
電影獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級36%，平均得分5.2／10<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/knock_knock_2015/ | title=Knock Knock (2015) | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=October 7, 2015 | archive-date=2017-11-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128025143/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/knock_knock_2015/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分53（滿分100），評價兩極<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/knock-knock | title=Knock Knock Reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=October 7, 2015 | archive-date=2018-01-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117192158/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/knock-knock | dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|Dread Central|Dread Central}}從滿分五分中給了電影四分，說：「我們的確有究竟是為了什麼而使社交媒體產生的一部家庭入侵電影（沒錯，它當中有一段出現社交媒體），應該讓你在一個夜黑風高的夜晚提供外人溫暖和住所要三思而後行」<ref>{{cite web |last=Gelmini |first=David |url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/reviews/109339/knock-knock-2015/ |title=Knock Knock (2015) |publisher=Dread Central |date=2015-07-02 |accessdate=2015-08-29 |archive-date=2015-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819090917/http://www.dreadcentral.com/reviews/109339/knock-knock-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

